  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>Enter the Mysterious World of Orbulon!</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ballbastic! is a game created to scratch the itch of hardcore gamers with an interest in games that are easy to learn but difficult to master. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Difficulties for all skill levels and ages.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you have never picked up a ball-roller before, or have been doing it all your life, BallBastic! has 185 levels across the spectrum ranging from the breezy tutorial to the brutal Expert mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like the starter levels are<i> too</i> easy? Up the ante with Survival Mode, where just one death ends your journey.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Push Your Speed to Its Limits!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/54428cb457413d30bbc1fba3f777872b.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=672 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/54428cb457413d30bbc1fba3f777872b.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/54428cb457413d30bbc1fba3f777872b.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources on Orbulon such as Trampolines and Speeders can be your best friends...or your worst enemies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Forge Your Own Path</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think within the box...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/6aceefa726dd88deab923ea7db910820.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/6aceefa726dd88deab923ea7db910820.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/6aceefa726dd88deab923ea7db910820.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...or disregard it entirely!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/0d5f1244541603258bc0e61164e44196.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/0d5f1244541603258bc0e61164e44196.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/0d5f1244541603258bc0e61164e44196.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pure, Instant Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No replays, no cutscenes. Whether you win or lose, you immediately get back into the action, never interrupting the flow-state of gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/5ad82980d1735c7589a2ec0adf211cdb.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/5ad82980d1735c7589a2ec0adf211cdb.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/5ad82980d1735c7589a2ec0adf211cdb.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Travel through harder-to-reach warps to skip levels!  </strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/1788717cd775e8125d7b24e749b35816.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/1788717cd775e8125d7b24e749b35816.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/1788717cd775e8125d7b24e749b35816.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go <strong>even faster</strong> with silver-bronze and platinum-gold goals, letting you warp forward.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Voiceover Industry Veteran</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring Brian Matt as the announcer; returning to form from narrating Super Monkey Ball games in the early 2000s. Brian Matt brings with him well over two decades of voiceover experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/e5f909c0e0a1618c7131979fea75e3b6.avif?t=1764650840\" width=200 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=74 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> Over Twenty Different Collectible Balls </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=74 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more difficult the ball is to obtain, the more stylish the effect that it brings to the table!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Control Supports</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a WASD Warrior or a Controlstick Compatriot, BallBastic! has you covered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Ready to give it a spin? Board the ship to Orbulon! </strong></i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>Enter the Mysterious World of Orbulon!</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ballbastic! is a game created to scratch the itch of hardcore gamers with an interest in games that are easy to learn but difficult to master. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Difficulties for all skill levels and ages.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you have never picked up a ball-roller before, or have been doing it all your life, BallBastic! has 185 levels across the spectrum ranging from the breezy tutorial to the brutal Expert mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like the starter levels are<i> too</i> easy? Up the ante with Survival Mode, where just one death ends your journey.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>Push Your Speed to Its Limits!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/54428cb457413d30bbc1fba3f777872b.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=672 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/54428cb457413d30bbc1fba3f777872b.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/54428cb457413d30bbc1fba3f777872b.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources on Orbulon such as Trampolines and Speeders can be your best friends...or your worst enemies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Forge Your Own Path</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think within the box...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/6aceefa726dd88deab923ea7db910820.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/6aceefa726dd88deab923ea7db910820.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/6aceefa726dd88deab923ea7db910820.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>...or disregard it entirely!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/0d5f1244541603258bc0e61164e44196.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/0d5f1244541603258bc0e61164e44196.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/0d5f1244541603258bc0e61164e44196.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pure, Instant Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No replays, no cutscenes. Whether you win or lose, you immediately get back into the action, never interrupting the flow-state of gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/5ad82980d1735c7589a2ec0adf211cdb.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/5ad82980d1735c7589a2ec0adf211cdb.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/5ad82980d1735c7589a2ec0adf211cdb.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Travel through harder-to-reach warps to skip levels!  </strong><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/1788717cd775e8125d7b24e749b35816.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=670 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/1788717cd775e8125d7b24e749b35816.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/1788717cd775e8125d7b24e749b35816.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go <strong>even faster</strong> with silver-bronze and platinum-gold goals, letting you warp forward.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Voiceover Industry Veteran</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring Brian Matt as the announcer; returning to form from narrating Super Monkey Ball games in the early 2000s. Brian Matt brings with him well over two decades of voiceover experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/e5f909c0e0a1618c7131979fea75e3b6.avif?t=1764650840\" width=200 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=74 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> Over Twenty Different Collectible Balls </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.poster.avif?t=1764650840\" width=74 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.webm?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428170/extras/172105915f137cd33dcfec8e002deabf.mp4?t=1764650840\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more difficult the ball is to obtain, the more stylish the effect that it brings to the table!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Control Supports</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you are a WASD Warrior or a Controlstick Compatriot, BallBastic! has you covered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Ready to give it a spin? Board the ship to Orbulon! </strong></i></p>",
